               <code code="34069-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED:</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Erythromycin Topical Solution USP, 2% is a clear, colorless liquid, which is supplied as follows: <br/>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>60 mL bottle with applicator NDC 52565-027-59 </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Store at 20° to 25°C (68° to 77°F); excursions permitted between 15° to 30°C (59° to 86° F) [See USP Controlled Room Temperature].</paragraph>
